snippet.title: Bird BnB Trailer
snippet.description:
Bird BnB is open worldwide! 🌏
Host a number of feathery friends & decorate your cosy tree in this newly hatched 🐣 mobile game! Cockatoo is ready to check in, are you?

Term & conditions apply, these are:
1. You gotta be a bird.
2. That’s it.

Download FREE on iOS and Android: http://onelink.to/playbirdbnb
